      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line for my brand and i want to make sure it feels legit. i don't want it to look like we're just making fun of people or doing some weird cultural appropriation thing. can u help me define what the 'authentic' urban aesthetic is right now? like what are the key vibes and styles i should look into so it actually hits right with that crowd?",
