      "content": "i see. so it's really tied to those specific neighborhoods and backgrounds. if i'm trying to design clothes that actually represent that life, what kind of specific themes or characteristics should i bake into the designs? like, in terms of the actual \"spirit\" or personality of that culture, what are the defining traits i should be leaning into to make the collection feel authentic to those communities?",
